### Get Character by ID
# Replace with actual UUID after creating a character
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{characterId}}

### Get books a character appears in
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{characterId}}/books

### Create a Character (with series and optional book associations)
POST {{baseUrl}}/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}",
  "name": "Frodo Baggins",
  "description": "Frodo Baggins was a hobbit of the Shire in the late Third Age.",
  "image": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/lotr/images/3/32/Frodo_%28FotR%29.png/revision/latest?cb=20221006065757",
  "bookIds": ["{{bookId1}}", "{{bookId2}}"]
}

